            <div id="articleThree">
                <!-- Article 3 -->
                <a href="https://tanksgoodnews.com/2020/05/26/jean-and-walter-willard/" target="_blank">
                    <img id="goodNewsThree" src="GN4.png" height="200px"></a>
                <h2>Back Together Again</h2>
                <p>After 69 years together, you might think Jean and Walter Willard would want a day apart -- not a
                    chance. Last year, Jean moved into a nursing home following a fall whilst her husband lived just
                    around the corner and came to visit her every day. When COVID-19 struck, nursing homes across the US
                    were placed on lockdown and Walter was unable to visit his wife for over a month. Following health
                    issues of his own Walter asked for special permission to move into his wife's nursing home. The
                    photos of their reunion are everything, and proof that love can survive a pandemic.</p>
            </div>
